{"calories":"810","carbs":99,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"This hearty, rustic meal is inspired by some of Chef Andrea’s favorite Italian cooking preparations. Charred broccoli is roasted with crushed red pepper and served over orzo pasta with a rich, flavorful tomato \u003ci\u003esugo\u003c/i\u003e, or sauce. White beans add even more texture and complexity to the dish, which is finished with a tangy Parmesan vinaigrette. Pair with a refreshing glass of white wine, and you’ll swear you’re in Tuscany.","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"f04c6ca8a1","fat":37,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/hero_2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/menu_small_2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/small_square_2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/medium_square_2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/24396/recipe_profile_page_2688_Charred_Broccoli_with_Orzo__Tomato_Sugo__and_Parmesan_Vinaigrette___